<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBi9_00124" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBi9_00124_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「<sampling type="start" />両親を温泉にでもやりたくて。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">特に母さんが疲れてるからね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「へえ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―でも一番の親孝行は、いい恋人を見付けることよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うるさい」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、爽香は由季をにらんでやった…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　夜中の電話。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　―布子の一番嫌いなものの一つである。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　夫にかかって来たにせよ、自分にかかって来たにせよ、大体ろくな話ではない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　しかし、出ないわけにいかないのは、河村も布子も同じ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　夜中の二時を少し回っていた。</sentence>
<sentence>いつもなら、布子だけでなく河村も一緒に目を覚ますのだが、今夜はさすがにぐっすり眠ってしまったとみえて、軽くいびきをかいている。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―はい」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、布子が出る。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「もしもし？」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あ、奥さんですか、吉本です」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いつも河村と組んでいる若い刑事だ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あら、どうも。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―主人ですね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ええ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">せっかくホッとしてるところ、起こしたくないんですがね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　吉本の口調はやや重苦しい。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「分りました、今起こします。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―あなた」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　軽く揺すると、さすがに目を開ける。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うん？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「吉本さん。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">何かあったようよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　河村は、布子と一瞬目を見交わした。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―もしもし、俺だ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、つい低い声になる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やられたよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、吉本が言った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「どうやら、今村は釈放しなきゃならんだろうな」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　河村は思わず目を閉じて、ため息をついた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どこだ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　河村に、布子がメモ用紙を渡す。</sentence>
<sentence>―河村が吉本と話している間に、布子は爽子の様子を見に行った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―よく眠ってる」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">と、呟くように、<quote>「お父さんに、『しっかりね』って言ってあげましょうね」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どうした？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、河村が顔を出す。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「よく寝てるじゃないか」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ええ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―お出かけね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　河村は首を振って、<quote>「<sentence>心配した通りだった。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">まあ、同一犯人とまだ断定できたわけじゃないが、まず間違いないだろう」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「今度は…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ＯＬ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">二十六歳だそうだ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「二十六…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">気の毒に」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ちょっとシャワーを浴びるよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">目が覚めるから」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「服を出しとくわ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　行きかけて、河村は、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「悪いな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">やっと休めると思ったのに」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「文句は犯人に言うわ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">気を付けて」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「分った」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　河村は布子を抱き寄せて、しばらくじっと目を閉じていたが、やがて息をつくと、<quote>「<sentence>さあ！</sentence>
<sentence>　今度こそ、取っ捕まえてやる！」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<sentence>と、自分を励ますように言ったのである…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おはよう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">と、爽香は台所へ顔を出して、<quote>「<sentence>―何してんの？」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　びっくりした。</sentence>
<sentence>由季が台所に立っているのである。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「たまにゃ朝飯でも作るか、と思ってさ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「いいのに。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">結構まめなんだ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「一宿一飯の義理」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ヤクザじゃあるまいし」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、爽香は笑って言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―あらあら」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、母の真江がやってくる。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「由季ちゃん、いいのよ、そんなことしなくて」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「やらしときなさいよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">やりたいんだって」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　爽香は、少なくとも由季がこんなに素直になって来たことを喜んでいた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ＴＶを<ruby rubyText="つ">点</ruby>けて、ニュースと天気予報を見る。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―おミソ汁作った」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、由季が言った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「食べな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">和風朝食だよ」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　爽香は、少し固い表情になっていた。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「またやられた」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「え？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「女の人、殺された」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　由季は、驚いた様子もなく、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やっぱりね<sampling type="end" />」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
